<p>The sacred vermillion Shinkyo Bridge spans the Daiya River and serves as the traditional entrance to Nikko's shrine and temple area. This iconic wooden bridge is considered one of Japan's three most beautiful bridges.</p>

            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Hours:</strong> Apr-Oct 8:30-16:00, Nov-Mar 9:30-15:00<br>
                <strong>Admission:</strong> Adults Â¥300, Students Â¥100
